videos.description: Wake Forest's Doral Moore leaps up and slams down the lob pass for the high-percentage bucket.
videos.headline: Moore throws down alley-oop for Wake

videos.description: Nigel Johnson avoids the defender in the air and banks it in to cap an 8-0 run for UVA.
videos.headline: UVA's Johnson banks in the tough transition layup

videos.description: Defense leads to offense as Bryant Crawford breaks up the pass and beats the defense down the floor for the dunk.
videos.headline: Crawford gets the steal and slam for Wake Forest

videos.description: Nigel Johnson gets the rare fast-break points for the Wahoos with a two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Johnson gets the easy breakaway dunk for UVA

videos.description: Virginia coach Tony Bennett says his defense and Kyle Guy stepped up in the 2nd half to lead UVA to a comfortable 59-49 win against Wake Forest.
videos.headline: Coach Bennett impressed with defense turning it around in 2nd half
